<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 00:32:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军在西岸行动中击毙伊斯兰圣战组织高级指挥官并逮捕 17 名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-senior-islamic-jihad-commander-arrest-17-in-west-bank-operation/0000018c-1c94-d9ef-abcd-1eb5c1940000</link><description>在以色列军队和巴勒斯坦恐怖分子之间的交火中，两名分别为 15 岁和 9 岁的男孩被打死。一名军方消息人士告诉《国土报》，两人向部队投掷爆炸物</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 22:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-senior-islamic-jihad-commander-arrest-17-in-west-bank-operation/0000018c-1c94-d9ef-abcd-1eb5c1940000</guid></item><item><title>从哈马斯囚禁中获释的泰国国民正在努力应对创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/released-from-hamas-captivity-thai-nationals-struggle-to-process-the-trauma/0000018c-1b77-dc03-a9ec-1f7f6f220000</link><description>获释的农业工人面临一系列特殊挑战，包括语言障碍和没有家人迎接他们。但他们很快就会在泰国与亲人团聚，许多人说他们想回到以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/released-from-hamas-captivity-thai-nationals-struggle-to-process-the-trauma/0000018c-1b77-dc03-a9ec-1f7f6f220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席军事审查员抱怨内塔尼亚胡的压力和解雇威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chief-military-censor-complains-of-pressure-threats-of-dismissal-from-netanyahu/0000018c-1b7d-dd4b-a38c-1f7f489c0000</link><description>几周前，内塔尼亚胡向首席军事审查员谈及收紧有关取消需要审查批准的材料资格的政策</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chief-military-censor-complains-of-pressure-threats-of-dismissal-from-netanyahu/0000018c-1b7d-dd4b-a38c-1f7f489c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在调查哈马斯声称比巴斯母子在加沙被杀的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-bibas-mother-and-sons-killed-in-gaza/0000018c-1c01-dc03-a9ec-1c7be0f40000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日 Bibas 一家被绑架以来，Shiri 抱着她的两个孩子被恐怖分子包围的视频被发布，他们已成为战争的象征</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-bibas-mother-and-sons-killed-in-gaza/0000018c-1c01-dc03-a9ec-1c7be0f40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的风暴即将来临</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-29/ty-article/.highlight/the-storm-is-coming-for-netanyahu/0000018c-1c2d-dc03-a9ec-1c7f8a450000</link><description>以色列的政治分歧在 10 月 7 日与哈马斯的战争开始时暂时被掩盖，现在又重新公开化。一场新生运动的兴起几乎肯定会演变成更大的运动</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-29/ty-article/.highlight/the-storm-is-coming-for-netanyahu/0000018c-1c2d-dc03-a9ec-1c7f8a450000</guid></item><item><title>释放具有以色列公民身份的巴勒斯坦囚犯导致阿拉伯以色列人陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/release-of-palestinian-prisoners-with-israeli-citizenship-causes-dilemma-for-arab-israelis/0000018c-1b72-dc03-a9ec-1f7bf7540000</link><description>几十年来，以色列政府一直拒绝在人质交易中释放具有以色列公民身份的巴勒斯坦安全囚犯。随着预计与哈马斯交换的囚犯名单公布，其中包括约 20 名以色列人，社区中许多人担心这是政府试图将他们与恐怖组织联系起来</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/release-of-palestinian-prisoners-with-israeli-citizenship-causes-dilemma-for-arab-israelis/0000018c-1b72-dc03-a9ec-1f7bf7540000</guid></item><item><title>意大利犹太人准备游行反对反犹太主义，拉比遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/rabbi-assaulted-as-italian-jews-prepare-to-march-against-antisemitism/0000018c-1b30-dc03-a9ec-1f7b041f0000</link><description>米兰当代犹太文献中心主席说，至少在过去十年里，我们在意大利还没有看到过这种程度的反犹太主义。自 10 月 7 日以来，意大利反犹太主义显着增加——这是全球反犹太事件激增的一部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 16:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/rabbi-assaulted-as-italian-jews-prepare-to-march-against-antisemitism/0000018c-1b30-dc03-a9ec-1f7b041f0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯前往以色列和约旦河西岸，争取延长加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-west-bank-in-bid-to-extend-gaza-cease-fire/0000018c-1b97-dd4b-a38c-1f9799ea0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯致力于防止以色列和哈马斯之间的战争在整个中东地区扩大，并帮助带头努力增加对加沙地带的人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 16:09:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-west-bank-in-bid-to-extend-gaza-cease-fire/0000018c-1b97-dd4b-a38c-1f9799ea0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境社区居民拒绝参加与内塔尼亚胡的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-gaza-border-communities-refuse-to-take-part-in-meeting-with-netanyahu/0000018c-1b0d-da36-a1de-5f2f571b0000</link><description>许多代表哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击中心基布兹的人士宣布，他们将拒绝与总理会面。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 14:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-gaza-border-communities-refuse-to-take-part-in-meeting-with-netanyahu/0000018c-1b0d-da36-a1de-5f2f571b0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么真主党不加入哈马斯对以色列的全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-hezbollah-isnt-joining-hamas-in-total-war-against-israel/0000018c-1aec-da36-a1de-5fefaa5a0000</link><description>“我们仍然需要时间……但我们正在逐步取得胜利”：真主党的哈桑·纳斯拉拉赞扬了哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击，但他并不急于加入战斗。对于真主党及其赞助人伊朗来说，爆发大规模地区战争的条件尚未成熟</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 13:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-hezbollah-isnt-joining-hamas-in-total-war-against-israel/0000018c-1aec-da36-a1de-5fefaa5a0000</guid></item><item><title>奥克兰市议会通过决议，呼吁加沙停火，但未谴责哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-29/ty-article/oakland-city-council-passes-resolution-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire-doesnt-condemn-hamas/0000018c-1ac9-d501-a58e-3ffd376d0000</link><description>一位与会者表示，该决议“对外交政策没有影响，但将有助于在奥克兰传播‘反犹太主义文化’”，而这座北加州城市应该“关注警务、住房和教育问题”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 13:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-29/ty-article/oakland-city-council-passes-resolution-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire-doesnt-condemn-hamas/0000018c-1ac9-d501-a58e-3ffd376d0000</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，自 10 月 7 日以来，大多数在美国的犹太学生对别人了解他们的宗教感到不安</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/most-jewish-students-in-u-s-uncomfortable-with-others-knowing-their-religion-study-shows/0000018c-1af6-da36-a1de-5ff726920000</link><description>一项新研究发现，自学年开始以来，近四分之三的犹太学生经历或目睹了与以色列-哈马斯战争相关的反犹太主义。 “这项调查中的数据展现了全国校园仇恨状况的令人不安的景象”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 13:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/most-jewish-students-in-u-s-uncomfortable-with-others-knowing-their-religion-study-shows/0000018c-1af6-da36-a1de-5ff726920000</guid></item><item><title>“我问他怎么不感到羞耻”：85岁的以色列人质说她在加沙隧道与哈马斯头目辛瓦尔对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/85-year-old-freed-israeli-hostage-confronted-hamas-chief-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel/0000018c-1ad5-d4e4-a1df-3edd611c0000</link><description>获释的以色列人质约切韦德·利夫什茨 (Yocheved Lifshitz) 是一位来自尼尔奥兹基布兹的和平活动人士，她表示，她在加沙地带被哈马斯囚禁的两周里“经历了地狱”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:42:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/85-year-old-freed-israeli-hostage-confronted-hamas-chief-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel/0000018c-1ad5-d4e4-a1df-3edd611c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么圣经中以色列的城镇里有狮子——作为掠食者，还是战利品？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-29/ty-article-magazine/why-were-there-lions-in-the-towns-of-biblical-israel/0000018c-1ada-d4e4-a1df-3edfd4890000</link><description>在特尔伯纳 (Tel Burna) 发现了一块狮子的趾骨和一块豹下巴，该地被确定为圣经中的立伯纳 (Libnah) 小镇，这是近东地区众多以大型猫科动物遗骸为特色的遗址之一。巨人杀手大卫声称自己杀死了一头狮子，但他能做到吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:42:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-29/ty-article-magazine/why-were-there-lions-in-the-towns-of-biblical-israel/0000018c-1ada-d4e4-a1df-3edfd4890000</guid></item><item><title>“我们同舟共济”：病毒视频聚焦 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中的阿拉伯-以色列英雄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/all-in-this-together-viral-videos-spotlight-arab-israeli-heroes-of-october-7-attack/0000018c-1a85-d3b6-adef-bbfdf4520000</link><description>以色列贝都因社区成员如何在哈马斯袭击期间拯救犹太人生命的故事并未得到充分报道，但一家非营利组织正致力于改变这一现状。其创始人希尔·诺萨茨基 (Shir Nosatzki) 表示，“当国家和军队不在的时候，阿拉伯公民却在支持犹太人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/all-in-this-together-viral-videos-spotlight-arab-israeli-heroes-of-october-7-attack/0000018c-1a85-d3b6-adef-bbfdf4520000</guid></item><item><title>Saqr 358 伊朗巡飞导弹瞄准以色列和美国无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/the-saqr-358-iranian-loitering-missile-targeting-israeli-and-american-uavs/0000018c-1ac5-d3b6-adef-bbfd2efd0000</link><description>真主党多次用先进的防空“神风特攻队无人机”瞄准以色列无人机。胡塞武装用它在也门拦截美国无人机</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:23:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/the-saqr-358-iranian-loitering-missile-targeting-israeli-and-american-uavs/0000018c-1ac5-d3b6-adef-bbfd2efd0000</guid></item><item><title>追随金钱：对哈马斯的新战争刚刚宣布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/a-new-war-on-hamas-has-just-been-declared/0000018c-1ad3-d501-a58e-3ff77c3c0000</link><description>哈马斯经营着一个庞大的海外商业网络，直到 10 月 7 日为止，该网络基本上都逃脱了审查。打击它将是战争努力的关键部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 11:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/a-new-war-on-hamas-has-just-been-declared/0000018c-1ad3-d501-a58e-3ff77c3c0000</guid></item><item><title>这些是周三从哈马斯手中获释的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-hostages-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-wednesday/0000018c-1ae4-d080-ad8f-fbe579560000</link><description>作为与哈马斯停火和囚犯交换协议的一部分，包括几名青少年在内的十二名人质被释放。四名泰国国民也被释放</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 11:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-hostages-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-wednesday/0000018c-1ae4-d080-ad8f-fbe579560000</guid></item><item><title>引入北约部队：以色列应为战后加沙提出的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bring-in-nato-forces-the-plan-israel-should-present-for-postwar-gaza/0000018c-16ef-dd03-a7ff-beffdd000000</link><description>以色列不能也不应该留在加沙。但当以色列的盟友问：接下来会发生什么？内塔尼亚胡和他的嗜血弥赛亚暴徒政府没有答案。我的计划是以北约干预部队和重启两国谈判为基础</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 11:46:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bring-in-nato-forces-the-plan-israel-should-present-for-postwar-gaza/0000018c-16ef-dd03-a7ff-beffdd000000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲穆斯林感到容易受到以色列-加沙战争日益加剧的敌意影响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/muslims-in-europe-feel-vulnerable-to-rising-hostility-over-israel-gaza-war/0000018c-1a29-d501-a58e-3f7d23200000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，欧洲的仇恨犯罪有所增加。“像穆斯林这样受到种族主义影响的人往往不敢向当局求助，因为他们害怕二次受害，害怕自己不会被相信或被认定为肇事者。”德国打击反穆斯林仇恨非政府组织负责人表示</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 11:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/muslims-in-europe-feel-vulnerable-to-rising-hostility-over-israel-gaza-war/0000018c-1a29-d501-a58e-3f7d23200000</guid></item></channel></rss>